Class ApplicationContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.upmc.components.AbstractComponent
      • fr.upmc.datacenter.software.applicationcontainer.ApplicationContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.upmc.components.ComponentI, AdmissionNotificationHandlerI

    public class ApplicationContainer
extends fr.upmc.components.AbstractComponent
implements AdmissionNotificationHandlerI
    The class ApplicationContainer contains 1 RequestGenerator who generate requests, in this context the ApplicationContainer asks the AdmissionController for available resources in the Computer the ApplicationContainer asks for hosting the application.
    Author:
    Hacene KASDI & Marc REN
